des: List of vegan restaurant options in Brooklyn. Includes addresses, phone number, and brief descriptions which can be heard from Alexa, and read in the companion Alexa app. To enable, say "Alexa, enable Brooklyn Vegan." Then to use, simply say, "Alexa, ask Brooklyn Vegan for a fact."
